doctype html
html
  title #{item.product}
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/3/w3.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto')
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css')
  style.
    html,body,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 {font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif}
  body.w3-light-grey
    // Page Container
    .w3-content.w3-margin-top(style='max-width:1400px;')
      // The Grid
      .w3-row-padding
        // Left Column
        .w3-third
          .w3-white.w3-text-grey.w3-card-4
            .w3-display-container
              img(src='#{item.image}', style='width:100%')
              .w3-display-bottomleft.w3-container.w3-text-black
                h2 #{item.product}
            .w3-container
              hr
              p.w3-large
                b
                  i.fa.fa-info.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-text-teal
                  | Item Description
              p #{item.description}
              br
              p #{item.description1}
              br
              p #{item.description2}
              br
              p #{item.description3}


          // End Left Column
        // Right Column
        .w3-twothird
          .w3-container.w3-card-2.w3-white.w3-margin-bottom
            h2.w3-text-grey.w3-padding-16
              i.fa.fa-dollar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-teal
              | #{item.price}
            h2.w3-text-grey.w3-padding-16
              i.fa.fa-map.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-teal
              | You can buy this at
              br
              | #{item.shop}
              br
              img(src='../images/map.jpg', style='width:100%')
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | Jan 2015 - 
                span.w3-tag.w3-teal.w3-round Current
              p
                | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Praesentium magnam consectetur vel in deserunt aspernatur est reprehenderit sunt hic. Nulla tempora soluta ea et odio, unde doloremque repellendus iure, iste.
              hr
            .w3-container
              h5.w3-opacity
                b Web Developer / something.com
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | Mar 2012 - Dec 2014
              p
                | Consectetur adipisicing elit. Praesentium magnam consectetur vel in deserunt aspernatur est reprehenderit sunt hic. Nulla tempora soluta ea et odio, unde doloremque repellendus iure, iste.
              hr
            .w3-container
              h5.w3-opacity
                b Graphic Designer / designsomething.com
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | Jun 2010 - Mar 2012
              p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. 
              br
          .w3-container.w3-card-2.w3-white
            h2.w3-text-grey.w3-padding-16
              i.fa.fa-certificate.fa-fw.w3-margin-right.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-teal
              | Education
            .w3-container
              h5.w3-opacity
                b W3Schools.com
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | Forever
              p Web Development! All I need to know in one place
              hr
            .w3-container
              h5.w3-opacity
                b London Business School
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | 2013 - 2015
              p Master Degree
              hr
            .w3-container
              h5.w3-opacity
                b School of Coding
              h6.w3-text-teal
                i.fa.fa-calendar.fa-fw.w3-margin-right
                | 2010 - 2013
              p Bachelor Degree
              br
          // End Right Column
        // End Grid
      // End Page Container
    footer.w3-container.w3-teal.w3-center.w3-margin-top
      p Find me on social media.
      i.fa.fa-facebook-official.w3-hover-text-indigo.w3-large
      i.fa.fa-instagram.w3-hover-text-purple.w3-large
      i.fa.fa-snapchat.w3-hover-text-yellow.w3-large
      i.fa.fa-pinterest-p.w3-hover-text-red.w3-large
      i.fa.fa-twitter.w3-hover-text-light-blue.w3-large
      i.fa.fa-linkedin.w3-hover-text-indigo.w3-large
      p
        | Powered by 
        a(href='https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/default.asp', target='_blank') w3.css

      h1 #{item.product}
      // form(role="form", method="post", action="/profile/#{item.id}?_method=put")
      tbody
        tr
          br
          td Where to buy: #{item.shop}
          br 
          td Item Price: #{item.price}
          br 
          td Item Description: #{item.description}